prompts.frontCover:
Front cover of a birthday greeting card, a humorous and lighthearted watercolor illustration of the two specific people from the reference photo 2c13af74-1727-45cd-85e9-a54f470454a7. The man on the left, with his distinct glasses, short dark hair, and wearing his casual polo shirt, is playfully trying to blow out a single, stubbornly lit candle on a tiny cupcake held by the woman. The woman, with her characteristic hairstyle and wearing her patterned top, looks on with a wide, amused grin, holding the cupcake just out of his reach. Their expressions are exaggerated for comedic effect. The background is a clean, off-white with subtle paper texture and soft, abstract watercolor splotches of festive colors like teal and coral. In the center, the text "Happy Birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, and flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire design is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
